cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SI 

The paper discusses attacks on deep learning systems that threaten their security and privacy. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and machine learning (cs.LG), specifically computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of metrics for evaluating attacks, which could also fall under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI).
